main event: A local resident observed a large, round unidentified object hovering over a field near Alto, Tennessee.
interesting points: The object was approximately 50-60 feet in diameter and had a metallic appearance with a soft glow from within.,The witness observed the object for about 10-15 minutes before it accelerated rapidly and disappeared.,The sighting was investigated by the U.S. Air Force as part of Project Blue Book.,A second report involved witnesses observing another luminous object on April 13th, 1966.,No sound was reported during either sighting.
